description: Rita’s has been the regional supplier of the finest Italian ice and the freshest donuts for generations, so when it comes to tasty refreshments, this cafe is one of the nation’s favorites. You’ll always find a sensational selection of fruity flavors; Lemon, Mango, Sour Patch Kids, and many more. When those Southwestern sun rays are beatin’ a little too strongly, you may need a delicious frozen treat from Rita’s, promptly.
name: Rita's of Albuquerque
